Interface IBean

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    IAddress, ICatalogue, IContact, ICustomer, IDiscount, IDocument, IField, IInventory, IInventoryHistoryRecord, IOrder, IOrderItem, IPerson, IPersonField, IPersonTemplatePage, IPersonWorkflowField, IStepConsensus, ITag, IVendor, IWorkflow, IWorkflowConsensus, IWorkflowField, IWorkflowStep
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    Address, Catalogue, Contact, Customer, CustomProperties, Discount, Document, Inventory, InventoryHistoryRecord, Order, OrderItem, PersonField, PersonTemplatePage, PersonWorkflowField, StepConsensus, Tag, Vendor, Workflow, WorkflowConsensus, WorkflowField, WorkflowStep

    public interface IBean
    IBean interface for converting java objects JSON Format.

    IBean interface need to implement all Bean classes for converting Java Object into ParamNetwork related format.

    IBean defines below categories of operations:

    • Based on bean getJSONLD class, it will return bean class JSONLDObject, if any error while converting it will return null, otherwise it will return JSONLD Object.

    • Based on bean getJSONLDString implemented class, it will return JSONLDObject as a String, if any error while converting it will return null, otherwise it will return JSONLD Object.

    Since:
    1.0
    Author:
    Jitendra Kumar Balla, ParamNetwork
